lead_paragraph: Stephan Jaeger shot a 12-under 58 on Thursday in the Web.com Tour's Ellie Mae Classic for the lowest score in major tour play.

headline.print_headline: Stephan Jaeger Shoots Record 12-Under 58 on Web.com Tour
